  <prompt>
    Thread `searchIndexName` (from `RecordSearchRequest.SearchIndexName`) through `RecordSearchService.cs` to its call into `IKnowledgeDeploymentService.GetSearchClientAsync(searchIndexName)`. Existing callers passing no value continue to fall through to the existing 2-tier chain (NFR-02 — backward-compat).
  </prompt>

